hopobject.body: How do you know each other? list of drugs and prices in india Underlying sales at the group rose 2% to £2.8bn in the first half of the year, slightly ahead of expectations, with good growth in Education led by North America and developing markets. Adjusted operating profit fell £50mln to £137mln, which included a £37mln hit from restructuring charges and investments to support new product launches in the second half.
